    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Basic Description:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Dice is a more challenging and precise puzzle platformer. You have 5 &quot;moves&quot; per screen that consist of; dashing, wall bouncing, placing platforms, etc. Use your moves wisely and precisely in order to reach the end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 300 hand crafted puzzle platforming rooms!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around a 10-13 hour first playthrough run time!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Very smooth and fun to play controls set that is easy to learn and hard to master!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the story of the character Triste who was deeply scarred by an event that happened in his teen years. All he uses to cope is food that he eats at his tent. His canned beans got stolen one day and it's your job to find the thief while learning more about Triste's backstory!</p>",
